<h1>Contribute</h1>

<p>If you find this software helpful and would like too see it continue to grow, please consider donating your time, energy and/or expertise by <a href="mailto:info@cibonfire.com">sending me a message</a> and letting me know how you'd like to help out, or just sending your suggestions.</p>

<p>If you like to get down and dirty with the code, you can fork the project on <a href="https://github.com/lonnieezell/bonfire" target="_blank">GitHub</a>, do some work, and shoot back a pull request.</p>